channel.description:
Yeah, yeah. Here it is again. Lol. I'll add others later.
Finally bothered added NPC's being total dicks to you. [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n1.jpg[/img] *The original* training area. [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n4.jpg[/img] Player talking. [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n2.jpg[/img] Godwars dungeon: [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n6.jpg[/img]
The sreen when entering the GWD portal: [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n5.jpg[/img]
Teleporting emote: [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/n3.jpg[/img]
Woo, Custom area.
Lesser demons:[IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/lessers.jpg[/img] How to get here: First off, Go into the Magic tab and select "Monster Teleport." Select Island, then head East to find a pit: [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/lessers1.jpg[/img] It is right here on your mini-map. [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/lessers2.jpg[/img] When you enter, You'll see some basic Dungeon Rats. [IMG]http://i478.photobucket.com/albums/rr144/Anfernio_/lessers3.jpg[/img] Credits to Palidino76 for giving me this area idea.
Yay, Joy joy.
Postive feedback only.
